responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "CD8EE9E8455229DA24B91AB2DBF67592", "Into the muck and mire in quest of the hag fed, strumming a tune to please the dead. Evil and stench repelled by his ode, he finally found the witch\'s abode. Perching high atop a crooked stump, he began to play his lullaby. \"How dare you approach! I\'ll have you for stew like the heroes before!\" As she grasped her essence shillelagh, she paused and smiled a bit. \"Your melody is sweet, and slumber calls. What have you done?\" The witch was overtaken by the sweet, sweet lullaby of wee ones.")
name: MADD_0007_TOF_Read_PriestessAndThePiper_14
